headline: Dell Stock on Pace for Best Month Ever. Why It Continues to Be a Tech Winner.
summary: Dell Technologies  stock was surging Friday after earnings, as the company’s ability to push through headwinds keeps investors excited.  Dell reported a knockout quarter after the stock market closed on Thursday, driven by a strong demand for the company’s artificial intelligence servers.  Dell gave earnings and revenue guidance for the year that handily beat analyst expectations.
